{"tid":1963870,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"撐手足 撐到底","createTime":"2020-04-08T12:05:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T17:57:14.000Z","uid":334646,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0f8b51abdc2f5fc78850b2c0405170b792276c19","tid":1963870,"uid":334646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T12:05:13.000Z","msg":"呢排每日都有大量手足上庭，而且大多數係還押手足。但願意旁聽嘅手足往往唔過百，願意等到囚車出黎支持嘅更加可能唔夠50。每一位被捕手足都係賭上自己前途同性命去換取香港嘅未來，既然而家停學點解唔出黎聲援下手足?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全港18區人鏈都組到，點解我地唔組個由法院到收押所嘅人鏈，送手足由頭送到落尾。一來可以比人足知道佢地唔係condom，二來又可以對住條馬路做文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4088c6ba4cbd345df2b4651b7aa9829dfb2d09f","tid":1963870,"uid":209644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T12:08:22.000Z","msg":"人鏈會有我"},{"pid":"7c9ed95b1735b28721f163b6b6195fcb4caa0eac","tid":1963870,"uid":334646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T12:38:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1cdd1be53ceb7a7bdc06553f7f4054746ab14b7a","tid":1963870,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T14:14:02.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n講咗好耐都無人理"},{"pid":"8d91a82069ca2cc53d17ac1c4e0d1eb4d6c08bca","tid":1963870,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T14:16:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb5cadeb75cf4bb8973b93188aba6d908fc371cf","tid":1963870,"uid":334646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T17:57:14.000Z","msg":"推，聽日法庭要人"}]}